        "destruction": "The *Liver Bloodstone* melts into a puddle of poison if a worshipper of Arazni willingly submerges the *Bloodstone* in a lethal contact or consumed poison, then licks the *Bloodstone* clean. Each creature in a 15-foot emanation is exposed to the poison that destroyed the *Bloodstone*, as if they\u2019d touched or consumed that poison.",
